### Maven Specific ###
.mvn/
mvnw
mvnw.cmd
# Ignore the wrapper jar specifically if not already covered
**/src/main/**/target/
**/src/test/**/target/

### Spring Boot & Logs ###
# This ensures that even if you use different log naming conventions, they stay out of Git
*.log
logs/
temp/

### Environment & Secrets ###
# Already covered in your list, but vital to keep exactly like this:
src/main/resources/application.properties
src/main/resources/application.yml
.env
.env.local

